Brute Force Detection
source="WinEventLog:Security" EventCode=4625
| stats count by Account_Name, src_ip
| where count > 5

Time-based Analysis
source="WinEventLog:Security" EventCode=4625
| bin _time span=5m
| stats count by _time, Account_Name

Account Lockout Detection
source="WinEventLog:Security" EventCode=4740